description: The Wi-Fi Network Diagnostics Cluster provides a means to acquire standardized diagnostics met­ rics that MAY be used by a Node to assist a user or Administrator in diagnosing potential problems. The Wi-Fi Network Diagnostics Cluster attempts to centralize all metrics that are relevant to a potential Wi-Fi radio running on a Node.
